lines.text: It must be awful to be in bed with a dead man.
Oh, I don't know. You get used to it after 3 or 4 years.
This geezer doesn't have anything I could catch, does he?
I doubt it. He has a bad heart and you haven't got a heart at all.
Hey, Paco. Do you feel lucky?
You ask that of someone who cleans up vomit for a living?
